snippet.title: Kensington Avenue in Philadelphia...Update on Amber before she enters rehab. Caught her in the Trap
snippet.description:
Amber gets tuff love shown to her in this video, plus a reality check before she enters rehab.
I heard on AML that Amber was going to rehab. then days later my wife and I while cruising down Kensington Avenue in Philadelphia we saw Amber in the Trap. So I got out of the car, walked right in the Trap and requested an interview with her to find out about her going to rehab and whats going on with her stomach. 
Sray tuned and watch this video and please keep Amber in your prayers 🙏.
